Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Er, well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.49,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You two!}Hai đứa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.36,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I get to give a speech at the wedding, right?}Để chị đây phát biểu ở lễ cưới cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.14,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{No, it's me, right?!}Không, phải là tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.39,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{As the groom's sister, it's me!}Chị là chị dâu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.89,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'm both the groom and \Nthe bride's boss. It should be me!}Tôi vừa là cấp trên của cô dâu và chú rể nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Me!}Chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.15,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Me!}Tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.74,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{It has to be me!}Phải là tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{No, no, me!}Không không, tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.97,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Me! Me!}Tôi! Tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Me! Me!}Tôi! Tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.90,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hard to say whether they get along or not...}Bọn họ có thân nhau không vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.21,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Me! Me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Me! Me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{So, which one?!}Thế là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.91,Main,Shinozaki/Shiori,0,0,0,,{Which one what?!}Ai cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:34.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, does Yutaka-san \Never mess with you, Hayakawa-san?}Nghĩ lại thì Yutaka không nói gì về em nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:41.17,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm not small or cute, after all.}À không, em không nhỏ với dễ thương nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.83,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You seem small and cute to me.}Với tôi thì em nhỏ và dễ thương lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.40,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Manager... listen...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.92,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{For favors at the ceremony,}Về buổi lễ kết hôn,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.58,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{we can give away these cute plates \Nwith a print of Shiorin on them.}chúng ta có thể tặng đĩa có in hình Shiorin này.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm "Shiorin" now...?}Shiorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.73,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait, what about me?}Còn em?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.66,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{No one cares.}Không ai thèm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Why not?!}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.53,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{The trend these days is to have people \Npick from a catalog, anyway.}Ngày nay người ta thích \Nchọn từ danh mục có sẵn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Don't encourage her, Manager!}Đừng có hùa với chị ấy nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.58,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Enough already!}Đủ rồi đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:23.84,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Come on, let's all head to the shrine together!}Thôi nào, viếng đền đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sounds good. I wonder \Nif there'll be food stalls.}Phải nhỉ, không biết có quán ăn không.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.68,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{You want one of these?}Có muốn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.62,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{No, I don't.}Không ạ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I sure hope so!}Chắc sẽ có thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.62,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{Wanna put the cat ears on?}Đeo tai mèo nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.30,Main - Top,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{No, I don't!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.42,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{They're so cute, though...}Dễ thương mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.97,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Never!}Không bao giờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, cotton candy!}A, kẹo bông gòn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.14,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:55.04,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.52,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:03.74,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:08.70,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:13.59,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.09,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:22.26,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:27.34,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:32.95,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:37.74,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:42.14,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:47.06,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:51.08,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.37,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.70,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Baby you're the sugar}
